{"tid":1282334,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"今時今日你仲講政治中立？","createTime":"2019-07-03T14:16:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T14:35:48.000Z","uid":41993,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f17d314e838d09014145701e30a4c13865d7480a","tid":1282334,"uid":41993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:16:30.000Z","msg":"今日晏晝食飯聽到隔離枱係到講71 有無出黎行<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你有無出黎遊行？（指著對面果個<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我街站<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁你呢（問佢隔離果個<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我  <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政 治 中 立</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：今時今日你仲講<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政治中立</span></span>？ 真係難聽過你撐建制<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁每個人都有佢嘅取態<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：好聽啲咪<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政治中立</span></span> 唔好聽咪牆頭草 擺黎擺去 見風使舵！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：⋯⋯<br />\n聽完之後我上網睇左吓 香港真係好多政治中立嘅港豬<br />\n但係諗深一層 其實真係唔應該話佢地豬<br />\n豬比人圈養 佢無得簡<br />\n但尼班人 係主動比人<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">馴養</span></span> 主動成為奴才 走狗<br />\n政治中立 可以係你嘅行為 例如醫生 護士<br />\n但絕對唔可以係你嘅立場 見到邊度有著數就衝埋去<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">仲衰過何君堯 何律師至少從一而終 表裡如一</span></span>"},{"pid":"7f5ab5f383eba72b50d5af67351ad280f5a60831","tid":1282334,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:17:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddafd7510b0429a0273534fd25c0c903f6347180","tid":1282334,"uid":98399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite